HEADWORD: Mediatorial
<hw>Me`di*a*to"ri*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to a mediator, or to mediation; mediatory; <as>as, a
<ex>mediatorial</ex> office</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Me`di*a*to"ri*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My measures were . . . healing and <qex>mediatorial</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mediatorship</ent>⟦br⟧
